text: Robinson Ekspeditionen 2019 is the twenty-first season of the Danish version of the Swedish reality television series Expedition Robinson. This season, twenty-two contestants are taken to the Philippines where, for the first time since 2015, two tribes compete against each other to win challenges and immunity.https://www.bt.dk/film-tv-og-streaming/robinson-ekspeditionen-vender- tilbage-med-stor-aendring After forty-four days, one of them will win and become this year's Robinson winner.https://kendte.dk/robinson-vender-tilbage- her-er-deltagerne/ The season premiered on 26 August 2019.https://realityportalen.dk/rcarticle/galleri-her-er-alle-deltagerne-i- aarets-robinson-ekspeditionen/ ==Finishing order== {|class="wikitable sortable" style="margin:auto; text-align:center" |- !
